title: good to go
text:
MY PROJECT IS GOOD TO GOO 
The name "My Digital Diary (Mini Todo App, Goal Reminder)" is clear, but it feels a bit long. If you want something more concise and catchy, here are some suggestions:

My Digital Diary – Simple and clean
GoalMate – A friendly goal tracker
Task Journal – Combines a diary and to-do list
Daily Goals – Focused on daily productivity
Mini Planner – Short and sweet
DreamTrack – For tracking dreams and goals
Would you like a name that sounds more professional, fun, or personal?
quote: Success is not final, failure is not fatal: It is the courage to continue that counts. – Winston Churchill
